Marsh & McLennan Companies - Wikipedia






















 






Marsh & McLennan Companies

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"Guy Carpenter" redirects here. For the Neighbours character, see Guy Carpenter (Neighbours).

Marsh & McLennan


Marsh & McLennan Headquarters at 1166 6th Avenue in New York City







Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: MMC
S&P 500 Component


Industry
Insurance brokers, professional services


Founded
Chicago, Illinois, U.S. (1905)[1]


Headquarters
1166 Avenue of the Americas,
New York City, New York, U.S., United States



